# NOTE: rag/index/embeddings.npz IS committed — the local hashing backend
# (agent/rag_local_embed.py) produces a small, deterministic, reproducible index
# (verified in CI via `python tools/build_rag_index.py --verify`), so vector recall
# ships live and airgap-safe. Only ignore ad-hoc per-developer index dirs:
rag/index-*/embeddings.npz
